FYPCoordinator - Class in Controller
This class represents a FYP Coordinator who is responsible for handling various tasks related to FYP project management such as changing project supervisor, allocating project to student, deregistering student from project, generating project details report, and viewing all projects.

Constructor to create a new FYPCoordinator object.
FYPCoordinatorModule - Class in UI
The FYPCoordinatorModule class is a User Interface class that provides a command-line interface for FYP Coordinator's functionalities.

Constructs a FYPCoordinatorModule with the specified FYPCoordinator.
